snippet: The former Baltimore Orioles ace Jim Palmer has put his three Cy Young Awards and two of his four Gold Gloves up for auction.
abstract: Former Baltimore Orioles ace Jim Palmer will auction his three Cy Young Awards and two of his four Gold Gloves trophies; other baseball news noted.
lead_paragraph: The former Baltimore Orioles ace Jim Palmer has put his three Cy Young Awards and two of his four Gold Gloves up for auction.
